Michael Alter, president of 
Surepayroll, says small businesses could benefit from Hurricane 
Sandy by offering services that support cleaning and rebuilding 
efforts. Alter talked with Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  and Vonnie 
Quinn on October 29 on Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays Advantage."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 09:42
 